data.description: Here's your chance for a beautiful custom-built brick home in Cedarview Estates. Features 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, office, living room and family room, 2 car garage on just under an acre. Granite kitchen counter tops, high end laminate throughout this home, gas fireplace, and small shed. This home has a park like yard with beautiful mature tree's. NEW HVAC, WATER HEATER, and SEPTIC PUMP.
